snippet.title: This Is Elon Musk's Girlfriend
snippet.description:
Everyone knows who Elon Musk is, the billionaire entrepreneur who is quite possibly a genius. But who is his girlfriend Grimes (aka Claire Boucher)?

At first glance, Grimes and Musk look like the most unlikely couple. However, they seem to make it work. Grimes is a quirky musician who certainly has a distinct and eccentric style of her own. She also has an unusual persona that often gets people's attention. They definitely are an intriguing pair.

Grimes was born in Vancouver, Canada in 1988. To find out more about Elon Musk’s girlfriend Grimes, keep watching this video.
